org.gbif.dwc

Class SimpleSaxHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.gbif.dwc.SimpleSaxHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler

    public abstract class SimpleSaxHandler
extends DefaultHandler
    A simple metadata SAX base handler that collects all character data inside elements into a string buffer, resetting the buffer with every element start and storing the string version of the buffer in this.content when the end of the element is reached. Make sure to call the super methods when implementing this handler!
